FBNQuest, Asset Management said the most effective and safest way to build wealth and increase net worth over time is to save and take advantage of compound interest and manage risk through diversification. Managing Director of the company, Ike Onyia, said the firm seeks to reorient investors from the short-term outlook and instant gratification approach by encouraging them to focus on the rewards of thinking beyond today and investing to meet specific goals in the future. According to her, the company’s goal is to focus the attention of its clients on the future benefits that come from discipline and sacrifice. “We guide our clients by helping them keep an eye on the big picture – their goals – and ensuring those goals become a reality. “The Beyond Today message seeks to redirect thinking towards the discipline and rewards that are to be gained by thinking and planning to accomplish future goals,” she said.  To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .